Challenge - offensive trick
------------------------------------------------------------
A swashbuckler can deliver a challenge in an insulting
manner. If the foe accepts, he will refuse to run away until
he feels his honor is satisfied. Generally this happens at
the end of the fight, or after a short time regardless.

A challenged foe can also be pressed with the press skill
while they remain your current opponent.

GL:  4
SP: 40
command:  challenge <target> (defaults to opponent if in combat)
duration: short
see also: press, flair
